48
00:01:42,370 --> 00:01:44,870
When I play this game, I can drive that into the ground.

49
00:01:45,340 --> 00:01:46,340
(You'd better watch out.)

50
00:01:46,470 --> 00:01:48,240
(Me?)

51
00:01:48,340 --> 00:01:49,340
(There he goes again.)

52
00:01:50,610 --> 00:01:52,839
(Ong was brimming with confidence during the punching game.)

53
