- Seong Wu. It didn't go in. - It came back up.

66
00:02:16,230 --> 00:02:17,439
- It didn't go in. - Ta-da.

67
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,576
(The machine stubbornly comes back up.)

68
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:19,939
(Mocking him left and right)

69
00:02:19,940 --> 00:02:21,470
(Popping up)

70
00:02:23,140 --> 00:02:24,140
(He's ready for his second try.)

71
00:02:24,141 --> 00:02:25,280
(His 2nd try)

72
00:02:26,610 --> 00:02:27,610
It didn't work.

73
00:02:27,710 --> 00:02:29,109
No. You have to press the start button.

74
00:02:29,110 --> 00:02:30,980
(You have to press the start button.)

75
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,849
He's out of energy now.

76
00:02:32,850 --> 00:02:34,049
He used up his energy.

77
00:02:34,050 --> 00:02:35,990
I already used up my energy.

78
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,120
Hey, you were supposed to press the button first.

79
00:02:38,790 --> 00:02:39,790
Show us.

80
00:02:39,790 --> 00:02:40,790
(His 3rd try)

81
00:02:41,590 --> 00:02:44,129
- Gosh, it went over 700. - Yes.

82
00:02:44,130 --> 00:02:46,200
It's very close to 800.

83
