That's it?

92
00:03:08,450 --> 00:03:09,649
- That's it? - Let me try again.

93
00:03:09,650 --> 00:03:10,989
- Try again. - Let me try again.

94
00:03:10,990 --> 00:03:12,559
Why? Your score is lower than mine.

95
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,730
Did that hurt your pride?

96
00:03:13,790 --> 00:03:16,090
(His 2nd try)

97
00:03:16,330 --> 00:03:18,460
- You can't beat me. - Gosh, this is hard.

98
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:19,860
(His 3rd try)

99
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:21,800
(He's in 2nd place with 762 points.)

100
00:03:22,070 --> 00:03:23,430
(Inhaling sharply)

101
00:03:24,340 --> 00:03:25,939
How many times will you try?

102
00:03:25,940 --> 00:03:28,040
Did losing to me hurt your pride?

103
00:03:29,340 --> 00:03:30,340
(Darn it.)

104
00:03:30,341 --> 00:03:32,580
(I'll never let you beat me.)

105
00:03:33,780 --> 00:03:36,350
(An angry, powerful swing)

106
00:03:36,780 --> 00:03:38,249
That one was pretty powerful.

107
00:03:38,250 --> 00:03:39,520
(Nervous)

108
00:03:42,350 --> 00:03:44,389
It's 802!

109
00:03:44,390 --> 00:03:45,996
(The barefoot guy leaves without turning back.)

110
00:03:46,020 --> 00:03:48,890
- You finally did it. - He finally scored over 800.

111
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:51,199
- He finally did it. - He couldn't...

112
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:53,299
- handle losing to me. - Hey, Ji Hoon.

113
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:54,346
(They'll play until Woo Jin wins.)

114
00:03:54,370 --> 00:03:56,270
I don't think anyone can beat his score.

115
00:03:56,430 --> 00:04:01,540
(That's how the game of Beat Park Woo Jin began.)

116
00:04:01,740 --> 00:04:03,779
- I see. It's 700. - I'm not even close.

117
00:04:03,780 --> 00:04:05,910
(Current scores)

118
00:04:06,010 --> 00:04:08,679
I think Ji Sung has to try this.

119
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:11,320
- Ji Sung has to do it. - I bet he can nail this too.

120
00:04:12,420 --> 00:04:14,790
(Forget the weak guy, Jirung.)

121
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,866
(Park Ji Sung for soccer, Yoon Ji Sung for the best punch)

122
00:04:17,890 --> 00:04:20,589
- Ji Sung is pretty strong. - Yes, he's hiding his power.

123
00:04:20,590 --> 00:04:21,659
- That's it. - He only walks like this.

124
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:22,660
(He uses the minimal energy when he walks.)

125
00:04:22,661 --> 00:04:23,929
- He's been saving his energy. - That's it.

126
00:04:23,930 --> 00:04:25,260
- Show us. - Let's go.

127
00:04:28,730 --> 00:04:29,730
(Pounding hard)

128
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:31,770
(Pounding hard)

129
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:33,770
(Surprised)

130
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:35,840
That crushed it.

131
00:04:35,841 --> 00:04:37,239
(He comes in 2nd place with 797 points.)

132
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,240
(Current scores)

133
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,240
(Did you see that, guys?)

134
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,449
(Unleashing his power)

135
00:04:41,450 --> 00:04:43,009
Ji Sung, you're in second place again.

136
00:04:43,010 --> 00:04:44,250
Don't get cheeky with me now.

137
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:46,150
(Falling down)

138
