139
00:04:48,890 --> 00:04:50,560
Let me try too, but I'm not good at this.

140
00:04:51,090 --> 00:04:53,059
- Let's go, guys. Let's stop. - Okay.

141
00:04:53,060 --> 00:04:54,460
- Good job. - That made me wake up.

142
00:04:55,290 --> 00:04:57,010
(Sung Woon is all alone in the playground.)

143
00:04:57,730 --> 00:04:58,730
That was fun.

144
00:04:58,731 --> 00:05:00,770
He quietly put it back down.

145
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:02,699
- Fine. Let him try too. - Gosh, no.

146
00:05:02,700 --> 00:05:04,199
- No. I'm not going to do it. - Do it.

147
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,799
- Come on, guys. He'll try it too. - No.

148
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,800
- I won't do it. - Sung Woon is going to try too.

149
00:05:06,801 --> 00:05:08,209
- I'm not going to do it. - Gosh.

150
00:05:08,210 --> 00:05:10,309
- I'm not going to do it. - Show us.

151
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:12,610
- Try it for fun. Give us a taste. - Yes. Show us.

152
00:05:13,210 --> 00:05:14,210
(Let me just get a taste of it.)

153
00:05:14,211 --> 00:05:15,611
- Nice. - That sounded pretty good.

154
00:05:16,250 --> 00:05:18,179
(He's in 5th place with 723 points.)

155
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:20,150
(I could've done better.)

156
00:05:20,450 --> 00:05:21,720
(Let me try again.)

157
00:05:22,320 --> 00:05:23,890
The hammer is as big as him.

158
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,959
The hammer is as big as him.

159
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:29,289
The hammer is as big as him.

160
00:05:29,290 --> 00:05:31,160
- He got this. - My gosh, he broke the record.

161
00:05:32,100 --> 00:05:33,100
It's 802.

162
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:34,929
(That's crazy.)

163
00:05:34,930 --> 00:05:36,010
He's in first place, right?

164
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:38,499
(He's also in 1st place with 802 points.)

165
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:39,599
(Current scores)

166
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,809
- That's Woo Jin's record. Right? - You're good.

167
00:05:41,810 --> 00:05:44,479
Woo Jin, I hit 802 points with just 2 tries.

168
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,039
You hit 802 points after 5 tries.

169
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,656
- But it took him only 2 tries. - It took me 2 tries.

170
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,509
I'm really good at hitting something.

171
00:05:49,510 --> 00:05:50,649
(1st place: Woo Jin, Sung Woon, 3rd place: Ji Sung, )

172
00:05:50,650 --> 00:05:51,719
(4th place: Seong Wu, 5th place: Jin Young, )

173
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,819
(6th place: Dae Hwi, 7th place: Jae Hwan, )

174
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:53,890
(8th place: Min Hyun)

175
00:06:04,130 --> 00:06:07,160
(Episode 5: A Classy Day)

176
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:11,900
Ji Hoon.

177
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:13,600
I brought this for you.

178
00:06:13,910 --> 00:06:15,870
(The perfect hoodie for Danjong's personal color)

179
00:06:16,270 --> 00:06:17,280
"How dare you?"

180
00:06:18,940 --> 00:06:20,380
Oh, I'm Jeon Mi Do.

181
00:06:20,510 --> 00:06:21,580
"Yes, Your Majesty."

182
00:06:21,910 --> 00:06:23,149
I went there and worked out a bit.

183
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:24,179
- So I feel better. - Really?

184
00:06:24,180 --> 00:06:25,980
- You worked out again? - I was really tired.

185
00:06:26,380 --> 00:06:28,900
- Did it boost your energy? - Yes, my blood is circulating now.

186
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,260
Should I play Euratgotcha?

187
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:33,559
- You have to scream "Euratgotcha." - After you play...

188
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:35,640
(You have to scream "Euratgotcha" when you play it.)

189
00:06:36,230 --> 00:06:39,029
- Euratgotcha. - Euratgotcha.

190
00:06:39,030 --> 00:06:40,400
Really? I won't do it then.

191
00:06:41,070 --> 00:06:42,929
Just scream "Euratgotcha." Come on, do it.

192
00:06:42,930 --> 00:06:44,339
I can't scream like that.

193
00:06:44,340 --> 00:06:46,370
We'll watch you from afar. Just shout.

194
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:48,240
(Daw Hwi, come here already.)

195
00:06:48,570 --> 00:06:50,010
(Tempted)

196
00:06:50,710 --> 00:06:53,110
I'll play Euratgotcha.

197
00:06:53,540 --> 00:06:55,809
Dae Hwi will play Euratgotcha.

198
00:06:55,810 --> 00:06:59,050
Dae Hwi is going to play Euratgotcha!

199
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:02,490
(What will Dae Hwi's version of Euratgotcha be like?)

200
00:07:03,490 --> 00:07:04,920
Euratgotcha.

201
00:07:05,590 --> 00:07:06,590
(Euratgotcha)

202
00:07:07,060 --> 00:07:08,660
(Standing straight)

203
00:07:08,860 --> 00:07:09,990
Where's your energy?

204
00:07:10,590 --> 00:07:11,629
(But the capsule still came out.)

205
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:12,700
Wait. What is it?

206
00:07:13,970 --> 00:07:16,999
- What's this? - Gosh, we have to take a test now.

207
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,940
(A test sheet is in the capsule?)

208
00:07:19,570 --> 00:07:20,909
(The item from Dae Hwi's capsule, )

209
00:07:20,910 --> 00:07:22,040
(a Wanna One test)

210
00:07:22,540 --> 00:07:24,679
(There are 20 questions about Wanna One.)

211
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,200
(Wannables, why don't you try it too?)

212
00:07:26,610 --> 00:07:28,149
- Gosh. - Let's take the test.

213
00:07:28,150 --> 00:07:29,150
- Guys, let's take the test. - Guys.

214
00:07:29,151 --> 00:07:30,849
Let's take the Wanna One test.

215
00:07:30,850 --> 00:07:31,879
It's the Wanna One test.

216
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:32,919
The Wanna One test.

217
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,789
Students, take your seats.

218
00:07:34,790 --> 00:07:36,219
Let's take the Wanna One test.

219
00:07:36,220 --> 00:07:37,520
The test was in the capsule.

220
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,760
(Everyone gathers around.)

221
00:07:38,860 --> 00:07:41,130
All right. When is Wannables' birthday?

222
00:07:41,630 --> 00:07:42,630
July 7.

223
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:46,160
- Is that the correct answer? - It is.

224
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:48,570
When is Wannable Kim Min Jung's birthday?

225
00:07:48,730 --> 00:07:50,629
- September 13. - That's correct.

226
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:51,999
How did you know that?

227
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,269
I know a bit about Kim Min Jung.

228
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:55,239
When is Wannable Park Min Young's birthday?

229
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,240
January 4.

230
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,240
(This is it for the warmup.)

231
00:07:57,241 --> 00:07:58,709
All right. The category is Wanna One.

232
00:07:58,710 --> 00:08:00,140
Here's the Wanna One test.

233
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,579
We'll have only ten minutes to finish the test.

234
00:08:02,580 --> 00:08:03,679
But there are so many questions here.

235
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:05,079
- No, this isn't a lot. Ten minutes. - It's...

236
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:06,249
Can we cheat?

237
00:08:06,250 --> 00:08:07,989
- You can't cheat. - We shouldn't sit together then.

238
00:08:07,990 --> 00:08:09,549
I'll do it in the back then.

239
00:08:09,550 --> 00:08:11,420
Okay. I'll move too.

240
00:08:11,860 --> 00:08:14,290
(Test Taker Type 1 is serious about security.)

241
00:08:16,430 --> 00:08:18,499
(Test Taker Type 2 covers up his answers with not much effort.)

242
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:20,506
We put down our birthday for the identification number, right?

243
00:08:20,530 --> 00:08:24,000
(Test Taker Type 3 leaves the answer out in the open.)

244
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:28,340
(The members take the test more seriously than expected.)

245
00:08:29,210 --> 00:08:30,940
Ji Sung, think about it.

246
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,640
Think about it.

247
00:08:32,641 --> 00:08:35,250
We couldn't have taken the test here if we hadn't had this table.

248
00:08:36,250 --> 00:08:38,019
(I'm such a cool guy.)

249
00:08:38,020 --> 00:08:40,720
(He suddenly remembers making the table.)

250
00:08:40,950 --> 00:08:42,489
Right. You did a great job with this.

251
00:08:42,490 --> 00:08:43,819
We would've been lost without you.

252
00:08:43,820 --> 00:08:45,120
(Satisfied)

253
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:46,389
The first question is tough.

254
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:47,459
Gosh, this is fun.

255
00:08:47,460 --> 00:08:49,659
"The fiery-hot buldak ramyeon."

256
00:08:49,660 --> 00:08:50,729
Come on.

257
00:08:50,730 --> 00:08:52,759
- Hey. How can we get this right? - I don't know.

258
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:54,799
- I can't answer the second one. - Hey.

259
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:56,200
"Wing."

260
